FT  16 APR 93 / World News in Brief: German workers demonstrate
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
About 91,000 German steel and engineering workers protested in the former
East German town of Erfurt against employers' cancellation of a pledge to
raise wages by 26 per cent from April 1. The employers say the 1991 pay pact
is no longer realistic.
