</XX>
<IN>P2326 Men's and Boys' Work Clothing.
    P5136 Men's and Boys' Clothing.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>FIN  Annual report.
    CMMT  Comment &amp; Analysis.
</TP>
