<HEADLINE>
FT  15 APR 93 / World News In Brief: Hang Seng surges
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The Hang Seng Index surged 371.53 to a record 6,789.74 on news of an end to
the Sino-British political deadlock. Page 4; Lex, Page 24; World stocks,
Page 39
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
