FT  14 APR 93 / UK Company News: Sykes-Pickavant lower at Pounds 629,000
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Sykes-Pickavant, the USM-quoted manufacturer of hand tools and diagnostic
equipment, reported another downturn in 1992 with pre-tax profits of Pounds
